{"tid":1379036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少少賽後分析，前線手足戰略要諗諗佢","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:22.000Z","uid":14153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91525256d256979be783530e1494e23fb99ab2b3","tid":1379036,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"利伸左先，我係睇直播觀察返黎嘅有幾點<br />\n<br />\n1. 太被動，四五點西環得廿幾個防暴，但全部開遮陣對峙<br />\n<br />\n2. 陣地戰守唔到，原因係冇方法擊退到對方進攻，當畜聾突擊，係街壘嘅手足們就應該飛下野去阻嚇佢地前進，咁先係有效防守<br />\n<br />\n3. 人企得太密，今晚人好多，但人多冇好好安排，反而係戰略缺點，令到前面退唔到，一個突擊走唔切就收哂皮<br />\n<br />\n4. 前線缺乏自衛手段，前期根本冇人運「物品」上去俾佢地還擊<br />\n<br />\n5. 手足們未夠放<br />\n<br />\n6. 呢個係個人見解，其實陣地戰對於裝備唔精良一方黎講冇利，示威者優點係機動、人夠多，更加應該將佢地分散開四方八面咁抽水突擊，咁樣會令具隊形嘅方陣兵疲於奔命，防不勝防<br />\n<br />\n面對堅壁清野，更加要四處流竄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e732b8ff5c30b088b3957611d1cd704ee78010","tid":1379036,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8989e00df296c22acca9e6ab3248f07c506898e8","tid":1379036,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"[策略][水戰］召集所有前線玩水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c93401d2e585d6fdbe5890463ebd16eabddff12","tid":1379036,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e3b0ec6f3117a531a277c59ec0e272fae8ffb","tid":1379036,"uid":64428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"收收皮先 又黎冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"24bc735ea5324bd970a6322153dfded34ad5fa01","tid":1379036,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" c